@startuml
title TestForge v1 — Estados da RecordingSession

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF

[*] --> Idle : CLI inicia

Idle --> Recording : start()
Recording : Captura eventos\n(pointerup, input, keydown)
Recording : Gera raw_events.jsonl
Recording : Coleta screenshots/DOM/AX

Recording --> Recording : Novo evento capturado\n→ append JSONL
Recording --> Paused : pause()
Paused --> Recording : resume()
Recording --> Stopped : stop()
Paused --> Stopped : stop()

Stopped --> Finalized : finalize()
Finalized : recording_metadata.json atualizado
Finalized : status = "completed"
Finalized : NAO aceita novos eventos

Stopped --> [*] : discard()
Finalized --> [*]

note right of Recording
  Durante Recording:
  - Cada evento persiste em raw_events.jsonl
  - Screenshots/DOM/AX salvos por evento
  - network_log.json em background
  - sensitive_data_alert.json se detectado
end note

note right of Finalized
  Apos finalize():
  - recording_metadata.json tem timestamps
  - Sessao pronta para MIS (normalizer)
  - Imutavel — nao aceita novos eventos
end note

@enduml
